<p>Before opening:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/issues?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;q=is%3Aissue">Search for duplicate or closed issues</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://html5.validator.nu/">Validate</a> and <a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootlint#in-the-browser">lint</a> any HTML to avoid common problems</li>
  <li>Read the <a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md">contributing guidelines</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Bug reports must include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Operating system and version (Windows, Mac OS X, Android, iOS, Win10 Mobile)</li>
  <li>Browser and version (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, IE, MS Edge, Opera 15+, Android Browser)</li>
  <li><a href="https://css-tricks.com/reduced-test-cases/">Reduced test case</a> and suggested fix using <a href="https://codepen.io/">CodePen</a> or <a href="https://jsbin.com/">JS Bin</a></li>
</ul>
